  <brief_title>Phase 2A Study of Setipiprant Tablets in Androgenetic Alopecia in Males</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Phase 2A Study of Setipiprant Tablets in Androgenetic Alopecia in Males</official_title>
  <sponsors>
