  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability and efficacy of the oral administration of
      setipiprant tablets 1000 mg twice daily (BID) relative to placebo in 18 to 49 years old males
      with androgenetic alopecia (AGA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
